Construction project managers (CPMs) should perform task related to the development of a management plan for their project including monitoring and control strategies. Should have a good understanding of the scope and familiar with the WBS and project schedule to ensure resources are available as needed. Cost components are also part of the tasks and roles a CPM should be familiar with. Skills include the ability to communicate with different stakeholders, manage risk, charisma and leadership, and stakeholderâ€™s management.

